null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed4a/5d96/345824_mini.png?m=1781020278", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed4a/5d96/345824_normal.png?m=1781020278", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed4a/5d96/345824_large.png?m=1781020278", "created": 1535628888, "last_modified": 1781020278, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "yorks", "last_touched": 1781057483, "title": "[记录帖] 朋友准备去泰国发展，这一趟不知道会怎样", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1219202", "created": 1781022135, "deleted": 0, "content": "起因是朋友在国内找不到工作，找了很久没响应，找的时间可能有 1 年了吧，也可能是手头拮据实在不行了，想去外面试试。\r\n\r\n看截图感觉不靠谱，劝过也说了风险点，截图用 gemini 问了一嘴，输出一堆风险。但是他还是想试试，只能给句生死有命富贵在天了。\r\n\r\n今天拉了个微信群，拉了家人和好友，一起充当后备安全站，出事马上 call 。\r\n\r\n我俩认识了有 10 多年了，是初中同学来的，只能感慨，希望他能顺利吧。\r\n\r\n以下是朋友和人事的截图：\r\nhttps://imgur.com/a/gqmWtZT\r\nhttps://imgur.com/a/4ZcJSof\r\nhttps://imgur.com/a/kwZU7OH\r\nhttps://imgur.com/a/i0lUJah", "content_rendered": "起因是朋友在国内找不到工作，找了很久没响应，找的时间可能有 1 年了吧，也可能是手头拮据实在不行了，想去外面试试。<br /><br />看截图感觉不靠谱，劝过也说了风险点，截图用 gemini 问了一嘴，输出一堆风险。但是他还是想试试，只能给句生死有命富贵在天了。<br /><br />今天拉了个微信群，拉了家人和好友，一起充当后备安全站，出事马上 call 。<br /><br />我俩认识了有 10 多年了，是初中同学来的，只能感慨，希望他能顺利吧。<br /><br />以下是朋友和人事的截图：<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imgur.com/a/gqmWtZT\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://imgur.com/a/gqmWtZT</a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imgur.com/a/4ZcJSof\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://imgur.com/a/4ZcJSof</a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imgur.com/a/kwZU7OH\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://imgur.com/a/kwZU7OH</a><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imgur.com/a/i0lUJah\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://imgur.com/a/i0lUJah</a>", "last_modified": 1781022135, "replies": 73, "id": 1219202}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_large.png?m=1644885960", "name": "car", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_normal.png?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 3248, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 2278, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 342963, "username": "wocanmei", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wocanmei", "website": "https://naosense.github.io", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "naosense", "btc": "", "location": "北京", "tagline": "你知道你知道的，但你不知道的你并不知道你不知道", "bio": "Java is good boy!", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4328/7ae0/342963_mini.png?m=1706141308", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4328/7ae0/342963_normal.png?m=1706141308", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4328/7ae0/342963_large.png?m=1706141308", "created": 1534755734, "last_modified": 1706141308, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "66beta", "last_touched": 1781057639, "title": "还是电车香啊！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1219229", "created": 1781051411, "deleted": 0, "content": "买车一年多了，目前跑了 15487 公里，充了 54 次电，除了刚提车时充了几次慢充，剩下都是快充。总共充了 2874 度电，花了 2369 块钱，平均一公里大概一毛五，这还是没有家充的情况。\r\n\r\n![充电概览]( https://naosense.github.io/2026/06/09/%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%BD%A6%E9%A6%99%E5%95%8A/%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E6%A6%82%E8%A7%88.png)\r\n\r\n这一年多，去了不少地方，淄博烧烤吃了，大明湖逛了，草原上撒欢了……，有车后活动半径确实大了不少，有事没事就去开一圈，一点都不心疼。有一次，闲着没事，大清早绕着五环跑了一圈。之前一直坚持摇油车，摇了好多年都没中也不愿换电车，老觉得电车不靠谱，现在我只能说电车真香，未来已来！\r\n\r\n![充电足迹]( https://naosense.github.io/2026/06/09/%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%BD%A6%E9%A6%99%E5%95%8A/%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E8%B6%B3%E8%BF%B9.png)\r\n\r\nhttps://naosense.github.io/2026/06/09/%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%BD%A6%E9%A6%99%E5%95%8A/", "content_rendered": "<p>买车一年多了，目前跑了 15487 公里，充了 54 次电，除了刚提车时充了几次慢充，剩下都是快充。总共充了 2874 度电，花了 2369 块钱，平均一公里大概一毛五，这还是没有家充的情况。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"充电概览\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://naosense.github.io/2026/06/09/%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%BD%A6%E9%A6%99%E5%95%8A/%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E6%A6%82%E8%A7%88.png\"/></p>\n<p>这一年多，去了不少地方，淄博烧烤吃了，大明湖逛了，草原上撒欢了……，有车后活动半径确实大了不少，有事没事就去开一圈，一点都不心疼。有一次，闲着没事，大清早绕着五环跑了一圈。之前一直坚持摇油车，摇了好多年都没中也不愿换电车，老觉得电车不靠谱，现在我只能说电车真香，未来已来！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"充电足迹\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://naosense.github.io/2026/06/09/%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%BD%A6%E9%A6%99%E5%95%8A/%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E8%B6%B3%E8%BF%B9.png\"/></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://naosense.github.io/2026/06/09/%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%BD%A6%E9%A6%99%E5%95%8A/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://naosense.github.io/2026/06/09/%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%BD%A6%E9%A6%99%E5%95%8A/</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1781051411, "replies": 62, "id": 1219229}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 11017, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2349, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 243325, "username": "intoext", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/intoext", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/16dc/e148/243325_mini.png?m=1688862810", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/16dc/e148/243325_normal.png?m=1688862810", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/16dc/e148/243325_large.png?m=1688862810", "created": 1500559674, "last_modified": 1688862810, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Arrowing", "last_touched": 1781019024, "title": "原来我们不由不觉地使用了好多病句，今天被娃鄙视了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1219045", "created": 1780984110, "deleted": 0, "content": "早上送他上学\r\n\r\n我说快期末了，你得把各月考的资料整理一下，把重点知识点该打印打印，提前未雨绸缪一下。\r\n\r\n他说，你这是病句。 未雨绸缪就是提前准备了。你还加提前。\r\n\r\n提前未雨绸缪是不对的。", "content_rendered": "<p>早上送他上学</p>\n<p>我说快期末了，你得把各月考的资料整理一下，把重点知识点该打印打印，提前未雨绸缪一下。</p>\n<p>他说，你这是病句。 未雨绸缪就是提前准备了。你还加提前。</p>\n<p>提前未雨绸缪是不对的。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780984110, "replies": 59, "id": 1219045}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 11017, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2349, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 686571, "username": "yiroonli", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yiroonli", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3ee84a74ba01ac19a27b946b339d1042?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3ee84a74ba01ac19a27b946b339d1042?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3ee84a74ba01ac19a27b946b339d1042?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1713944677, "last_modified": 1780985148, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "youjiji", "last_touched": 1781015348, "title": "关于很久没见过面的朋友借钱", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1219053", "created": 1780985226, "deleted": 0, "content": "偶尔会在微信上聊几句，相隔也不远，但好多年没见过面。\r\n\r\n突然发微信向我借钱，二万块。\r\n\r\n我想：他有哥哥，有许多其他更好的朋友，不借，跑来跟我一个很久没见面，甚至连他现在生活怎样也不知道的朋友借钱，难道支付宝，京东这些容易借的平台借不到吗？他说月底 20 发工资还我，但我想一下，他好像工资也不到这个数啊，还有房贷要还，他真的能在发工资的时候还给我吗？\r\n\r\n大家觉得，我该借吗？不借，又有什么好的拒绝借口呢？", "content_rendered": "偶尔会在微信上聊几句，相隔也不远，但好多年没见过面。<br /><br />突然发微信向我借钱，二万块。<br /><br />我想：他有哥哥，有许多其他更好的朋友，不借，跑来跟我一个很久没见面，甚至连他现在生活怎样也不知道的朋友借钱，难道支付宝，京东这些容易借的平台借不到吗？他说月底 20 发工资还我，但我想一下，他好像工资也不到这个数啊，还有房贷要还，他真的能在发工资的时候还给我吗？<br /><br />大家觉得，我该借吗？不借，又有什么好的拒绝借口呢？", "last_modified": 1781046541, "replies": 49, "id": 1219053}]